59:23.300 --> 59:30.820
cause remains mathematically identical. We are brilliantly complex, multi-dimensional beings, naturally adapted to

59:30.820 --> 59:35.940
operate in high-dimensional contexts, who are currently being forcibly violently compressed into

59:35.940 --> 59:44.180
one-dimensional scalar metrics by the systems we rely on. The thermometer simply cannot taste the complexity of the meal,

